data.title: Went to pick up lunch!
data.text: Super friendly!  The line goes quick!  The staff was friendly, store was clean and there was open parking spots.

data.title: I freaked, every time
data.text: Fast, fresh, fun, friendly, and fantastic food. You can get in "line" and get your food ten times in the time the Chipotle line takes.

data.title: Consistently good - but won't deliver less than a mile from restuarant
data.text: Our office orders from Jimmy Johns quite often and our office complex more than weekly. Really like the Unwraps. Called on Sunday for a delivery and was told that we are too far away and that it was a new decision of management to not deliver to The Lakes housing development nor our office complexes any longer. She said it was a decision of management and they are getting alot of complaints. Hopefully they will rethink this decision.

data.title: Not my cup of tea
data.text: I am not a huge fan of jimmy johns since there isn't a huge variety of toppings and if you want certain ones you have to pay. My main issue is when I order it to-go FREAKY FAST doesn't happen I waited 45 minutes for my order when the location is across the street from my place of work. I have a hard time going back to a fast food restaurant if I continuously have reoccurring issues.

data.title: Love the Sub
data.text: Love the bread and love the Turkey sub.  Super fast service, even when delivered.  Always a staple for our family.
